## File Structure Changes

```
~/.meeting-agent/
├── config.json
├── speakers.json                    # NEW: Speaker database
├── models/                          # NEW: Pre-trained models
│   ├── segmentation/
│   │   └── pyannote-3.0.onnx
│   └── embedding/
│       └── 3dspeaker.onnx
└── meetings/{uuid}/
    ├── meeting.json
    ├── transcript.json              # Enhanced with speaker_id fields
    ├── speakers.json                # NEW: Meeting-specific speaker mapping
    └── audio.mp3
```

